{"tid":1712421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有美英藉就打電話話自己身處中大啦, 醒少少得唔得呀.","createTime":"2019-11-12T14:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T15:38:49.000Z","uid":280088,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2a3b6308d712efdd2c7b9b0fafc922b5c1b76a","tid":1712421,"uid":280088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:19:17.000Z","msg":"唔係一定要讀中大先身處中大架ma, 屌你老母人地set 到出手條line咁低,你班柒頭仲係on99咁係中大搵人.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫下困在大學的外國籍手足，請聯絡領事館求助！<br />\nPlease call the following Consulates to help out the exchange students! <br />\n<br />\n美國 US：＋852 2523-9011<br />\n<br />\n加拿大 CA: +1 613 996 8885, (852) 3719-4700, (852) 2867-7348<br />\n<br />\n英國UK：+852 2901 3000<br />\n<br />\n德國Germany：+852 2105 8788, <br />\nEmergency contact for German nationals outside the Consulate General's office hours (no visa information!): <br />\n+86 (0)10 8532 9202<br />\n<br />\n法國French：+852 3752 9900<br />\n<br />\n澳大利亞 Australia： please contact the 24 hour Consular Emergency Centre on +61 2 6261 3305 or SMS +61 421 269  080<br />\n<br />\n意大利 Italy: +852 91315535<br />\n<br />\n日本駐香港總領事館 Japan +852 2522 1184<br />\n<br />\n大韓民國駐香港總領事館 South Korea +8522529 4141<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓 Philippines: 9155 4023 (24/7)<br />\n<br />\n台灣 Taiwan：800-0885-0885<br />\n<br />\n印尼 Indonesia: 3651 0200 (office hour only)<br />\n<br />\n新加坡 Singapore：65-63798800/8855<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞 Malaysia: +852 69006390 (WhatsApp/wechat only)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*唔好得把口，和理非！！forward照做！！！用你1分鐘！！！救人呀！！！*"},{"pid":"4466521a6be1f81f77be58137ec895158e7c8752","tid":1712421,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b7f38da77ee7234bbe1be72d627aadbefca096c","tid":1712421,"uid":221919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5af58c1cfce885b9fef110c76bf68352662149","tid":1712421,"uid":121869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:21:58.000Z","msg":"我想講一講既係防暴分區唔係用18區<br />\n而係港島、東九、西九、新界南、新界北<br />\n<br />\n暴大所在既沙田, 屬於新界南<br />\n如果想用區暴動去救佢的話<br />\n可以吹雞 荃+葵+青+東涌+沙+馬+火炭呢啲集中暴動<br />\n拉對角線最長距離去打<br />\n<br />\n其他區保持有零散開花去迫佢留住兵力<br />\n<br />\n而家集中晒沙田大埔<br />\n沙田屬新界南<br />\n大埔屬新界北<br />\n只會被兩區輕取....<br />\n就算十八區開花要開得有智慧<br />\n//<a href=\"https://t.me/hknimC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FhknimC%2F&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7cjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=e53c97d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hknimC/</a>"},{"pid":"b716ca93c25afd367c888b42138269fbe9c0564d","tid":1712421,"uid":391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:22:03.000Z","msg":"冷氣軍師夠鐘出場喇<br />\n開32台較大聲少少 打去領事館"},{"pid":"dd2c3b09b429629300582710d3a7ba5d92c86b10","tid":1712421,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:22:27.000Z","msg":"遠水不能救近火！！只係各地開花，班狗可以用無警時份唔理你！！<br />\n<br />\n分頭行事！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">主力反包！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">擋水炮車！！</span><br />\n另小隊開花！嘗試分散警力！做得幾多得幾多</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中大地理難去，但去到就去！人多就咩都有可能！求下大家！！"},{"pid":"cdd2b956ad838e1152ded5a9b4bbe1c06fc01308","tid":1712421,"uid":328267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"1ff671a8fb2a3ff53d4c6447f0ed891880c52b0e","tid":1712421,"uid":5801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c7e3746e378414422c8b2f77064ee610e6caf9","tid":1712421,"uid":40164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:22:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b79c2253a89d1853c1ca9a1a2756